description:
How do you identify a true prophet? What does the Bible say are the characteristics of a true prophet so we can avoid being deceived? Are there modern manifestations of the true gift of prophecy? What does the Bible reveal on this issue? According to Revelation 12 and 14, one of the distinguishing features of the organization that opposes Satanâ€™s kingdom is that it has the testimony of Jesus, the Spirit of Prophecy. Does God still speak through prophets today? Among the array of prophets claiming to have messages from God, is there a voice that really comes from the throne of grace? Learn about Ellen G. White and the Spirit of Prophecy in this episode.
